Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Located on the lower level of estate

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located in the booming industrial precinct of Mount Kuring-Gai Unit 6/22 Beaumont Road is a rare offering of this size. With a versatile 90/10 split of warehouse and office shares space on the sought after lower level of the Gateway Estate with the office boasting sweeping valley views.

Surrounded by high profile companies such as Universal Candy and Baden P Morris this is an offering that will not last long and is a must see.


Property Highlights:
- High clearance warehouse/excellent cubic capacity
- Ample parking
- Corner Unit
- Moments to M1
- Loading Bay
- Valley Views
- Amenities in warehouse and office

For more information and to arrange an inspection contact exclusive CBRE agents.

Located only six minutes from Wahroonga interchange with M1 and NorthConnex and Pennant Hills Road. 
Easy access to Sydney's north and north-west growth areas, the Central Coast and Newcastle.

The estate features office and warehouse units, all units have mezzanine office floors with balconies and bushland vistas. The total estate comprises 45,000 m² in four buildings with 8+ metre roof height and clear span floor areas. Level estate with 15m wide circular access road system suitable for B-Doubles and ample room for 40ft container handling

The subject unit has a structural mezzanine installed within the warehouse (which can be removed), the office area is fitted out with perimeter offices and large boardroom and brand new air conditioning, ready for occupation!

The unit breakdown is:
Warehouse: 1,290sqm
Office: 250sqm
Total: 1,540sqm
Parking: 15 car spaces (approx, as per strata plan)

Available for occupation from1 March 2021, long lease terms available.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: MOUNT KURING-GAI, OFFICE + HIGH CLEARANCE WAREHOUSE UNIT

Gateway Estate is located in the heart of Mt Ku-Ring-Gai Industrial area, within close proximity to Mt Ku-Ring-Gai train station, 3 kilometres* to the M1 motorway on-ramp and 1 kilometre* to the Pacific Highway.

Mt Ku-Ring-Gai now benefits from the NorthConnex Tunnel linking the M1 and the M2 motorway. This will drastically reduce travel times between Mt Ku-Ring-Gai and Western Sydney. 

For Lease is a 100% warehouse unit

+ Flexible warehouse areas from 800sqm* – 1,200sqm*
+ 7 to 8.7m* internal warehouse clearance 
+ 40ft container access
+ Flexible terms on offer
+ ESFR sprinklered
+ Small 20sqm* office built within the warehouse
+ Available immediately

For further details, please contact exclusive agent Ben Byford or Peter Mangraviti
